<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc0"><span>Calibri's Mega Cool SCP Logo Variants</span></h1>
<p>Do you see that cool logo on the top left of the page? Yeah, I know. You wish it was <em>even cooler</em>. Well, I'm here to help. Below are a bunch of various logos, which you can use to replace the stand one in the corner up there. Simply copy and paste the code for what you need, and you're golden!</p>
<p>Some of these are more inclined for various articles, such as the joint Foundation/GoI logos. Others, like the flag logos, are just for fun, to add a bit of a personal touch to your articles.</p>
<p>All of these logos are created by me, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606787022" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;">Calibri Bold</a></span>, unless otherwise stated. If you'd like to request I make a logo to feature on this, feel free to PM me! Alternatively, if you've made a logo that you'd like others to have access to, you may PM me a request for it to be featured on this page and credited to you.</p>
</div>
